\c 2
\s Vapristi vanotukwa naJehovha
\p
\v 1 Zvino ikozvino, vapristi, murairo uyu ndewenyu.
\v 2 Kana musingateereri, uye kana mukasaisa mumoyo, kupa rukudzo kuzita rangu, anoreva Jehovha wehondo, ndatuma chakatukwa kurwisana nemwi, uye ndatuka maropafadzo enyu, hongu, ndazvituka, nokuti hamuzviisi mumoyo.
\v 3 Tarirai, ndichaodza chizvarwa chenyu, nekumwaya ndove pamber pezviso zvenyu, ndove yemabiko enyu, uye ndichakubvisai pamwe nayo.
\v 4 Zvino muchaziva kuti ndakutumirai murairo uyu, kuti sungano yangu ive naRevhi, anoreva Jehovha wehondo.
\v 5 Sungano yangu navo yaiva kwaari upenyu nerugare, uye ndakavapa kutya kwavakanditya nako, uye vakatya pamberi pezita rangu.
\v 6 Murairo wechokwadi waiva mumuromo make, uye uipi hauna kuwanikwa pamiromo yake, wakafamba neni murugare nemukururama, uye wakatendeusa vazhinji kubva pauipi.
\v 7 Nokuti miromo yemupristi inochengetedza ruzivo, uye murairo vakatsvaka pamuromo wake, nokuti iye mutumwa waJehovha wehondo.
\v 8 Asi imwi makatsauka kubva panzira; makagumbusa vazhinji pamurairo; makasvibisa sungano yaRevhi, anoreva Jehovha wehondo.
\v 9 Naizvozvo ndakakuitai vanozvidzwa nevari pasi pamberi pevanhu vese sezvamusina kuchengeta nzira dzangu, asi makagamuchira zviso pamurairo.
\p
\v 10 Ko isu tese hatina baba vamwe here? Haasi Mwari umwe wakatisika here? Tinogonyengerana neiko umwe neumwe hama yake, tichimhura sungano yamadzibaba edu?
\v 11 Judha vakanyengera, chinhu chinonyangadza chaitwa pakati paIsraeri napaJerusarema; nokuti Judha vakamhura nzvimbo tsvene yaJehovha, inodikanwa naye, vakawana mukunda wamwari wavatorwa.
\v 12 Munhu anoita zvakadai, Jehovha achamubvisira pamatende aJakove, anodana neanopindura, neanovigira Jehovha wehondo zvipiriso.
\v 13 Munoitawo izvozvi munofukidza aritari yaJehovha nemisodzi, nokuchema, nokugomera, naizvozvo haacharangariri chipo, kana kuchigamuchira nomufaro pamaoko enyu.
\p
\v 14 Kunyange zvakadaro munoti: Nemhaka yeiko? Nokuti Jehovha akange ari chapupu pakati pako nomukadzi woujaya hwako, wawakanyengera, kunyange ari shamwari yako, nomukadzi wako wawakaita sungano yako naye.
\v 15 Ko haana kuita umwe chete, kunyange akange ane umwe Mweya wakasara here? Zvino wakaitireiko umwe chete? Wakatsvaka rudzi rwaMwari. Saka chenjererai mweya yenyu, kurege kuva neumwe anonyengera mukadzi woujaya hwake.
\v 16 Nokuti ndinovenga kurambana ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha, Mwari waIsraeri uye munhu anofukidza nguvo yake nokumanikidza ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha wehondo; saka chenjererai mweya yenyu, kuti murege kunyengera.
\p
\v 17 Makanetsa Jehovha namashoko enyu. Kunyange zvakadaro munoti: Takamunetsa neiko? Pakutaura kwenyu, muchiti: Umwe neumwe anoita zvakaipa, vakanaka pamberi paJehovha, ndivo vaanofarira, kana: Mwari wezvakarurama aripiko?